Source: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Section: javascript
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Docker Hardened Images <dhi@docker.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.7.0

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ca-certificates
Provides: nodejs (= ${binary:Version})
Conflicts: nodejs, nodejs-22, nodejs-24, nodejs-25, nodejs-26
Replaces: nodejs
Description: Node.js JavaScript runtime @MAJOR_VERSION@ (@TRAIN@)
 Node.js is an event-based server-side JavaScript engine built on Chrome's
 V8 JavaScript engine. This package provides the Node.js @MAJOR_VERSION@.x
 release line (@TRAIN@).

Package: @PACKAGE_NAME@-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: @PACKAGE_NAME@ (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Provides: libnode-dev
Conflicts: libnode-dev
Replaces: libnode-dev
Description: Node.js development headers @MAJOR_VERSION@ (@TRAIN@)
 Development headers for building native Node.js addons.
 This package provides headers for the Node.js @MAJOR_VERSION@.x
 release line.
